Package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.corfu.mapper

Class PayloadField

java.lang.Object
org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.corfu.mapper.PayloadField
public class PayloadField extends Object
Represents a field in a CorfuPayload. On creation, it extracts the annotated information on the payload field. It serializes and deserializes the associated field on a Corfu message from their binary format into a JsonMessage format and back.
